name: Ellie Williams TLOU2 Embedding
description:
A TI of Ellie Williams from TLOU 2. Wanted to see what would happen bringing in a game character and then putting it through all the great models on here. There are differing results but I think Ellie comes through in most of them. Results will likely be variable though.

Likely need to inpaint her scars etc

I used the same prompt and seed for many of these promos to show differences between the models.

Trained for 0.005:200, 0.001:400, 0.0001:1000, Batch 5 on 15 images
